snippet.title: 「KNUCKLE SANDWICH」Kickstarter Teaser
snippet.description:
🙇‍♂️ Join the discord! https://discord.gg/FRHQzdx

That's right, it's another video for your new favourite RPG, Knuckle Sandwich. Help support the completion of the game by backing the Kickstarter: http://bit.ly/knuckle-sandwich

Song: "Stinky Boy Strut" by Nelward https://soundcloud.com/nelward/stinky-boy-strut
